{"tid":1041730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣　一年一度　搗毀專制獨裁圖騰　砍蔣介石銅像","createTime":"2019-03-01T05:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T05:50:21.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd614044e705767da287b2f57c1603f039ae188","tid":1041730,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3643623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fch%2Fnews%2F3643623&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=553646d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3643623</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnimage.taiwannews.com.tw/photos/shares/CNA/20190222/20190222000018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fphotos%2Fshares%2FCNA%2F20190222%2F20190222000018.jpg&h=46560aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政大蔣中正騎馬銅像遭鋸馬腳<br />\n<br />\n政大後山的蔣介石騎馬銅像的馬腳被學生砍斷，引起網友激烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n砍斷蔣介石騎馬銅像馬腳的學生發佈聲明指出，這是為了抗議以前獨裁時期對人民的壓迫，並敦促政府儘快進行轉型正義。<br />\n<br />\n對此行為，政大學生反應熱烈，有人說馬是無辜的，為什麽不砍蔣介石的腳，還有人說這樣以後就不能看蔣介石的馬換腳站了，相當幽默。"},{"pid":"d57c4e4d2a4d9259a60a8e5926856d94b46880c8","tid":1041730,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d台仔真係弱智<br />\n年年都消費228"},{"pid":"ad995d86aa1b12ce90b50383a428a24e8ec59722","tid":1041730,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"中華民國已成過去，兩蔣遺物應必消除，轉型正義乃大勢所趨！"},{"pid":"cfeb86295ed219fcb2c597da791294e704615405","tid":1041730,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"問過南部未？"}]}